ponents/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#with-action","content":"Pass a `Button` to the `actions` slot to give the user a clear path to resolve the alert."},"41":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-17","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"Key"},"42":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-18","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"Description"},"43":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-19","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"`Tab`"},"44":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-20","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"Moves focus to the dismiss button or action button"},"45":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-21","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"`Space` / `Enter`"},"46":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-22","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#keyboard","content":"Activates the focused button"},"47":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-23","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#screen-readers","content":"The alert container uses `role=\"alert\"`, which creates an ARIA live region. When an alert is rendered or its content changes, screen readers announce the message automatically — the user does not need to navigate to the alert to hear it."},"48":{"id":"/docs/components/alert-24","page_id":"/docs/components/alert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/alert#dismiss-button-label","content":"The dismiss button defaults to `aria-label=\"Close\"`. Override it via `ariaLabels={{ close: '...' }}` to provide more specific context for screen readers (e.g. `\"Dismiss payment warning\"`). This is especially useful when multipl